STL TECHNOLOGY C said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 41.08% to NT$248,439,000 from NT$421,644,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales            248,439          421,644    
YOY%             -41.08%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,368,026        2,872,644   
YOY%             -52.38% 
=================================================================
 